story that will keep you in suspense until the very end.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The New Year's holiday will turn into a real nightmare for the main character.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Realistic sound design that will give you goosebumps.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3387120/extras/69f1553b5405f0378dff820f6b6f5cfa.poster.avif?t=1735040020\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3387120/extras/69f1553b5405f0378dff820f6b6f5cfa.webm?t=1735040020\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3387120/extras/69f1553b5405f0378dff820f6b6f5cfa.mp4?t=1735040020\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><i>The average time to complete the game is 30-40 minutes.</i></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i><u>Note:</u></i></strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i><u>There is no menu or any settings in the game except for changing the language...</u></i></strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i><u>You can exit the game by pressing ALT+F4 or by clicking on the painting in the starting room...</u></i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
